Thank you for understanding
how much he needs me.


900
01:02:50.403 --> 01:02:51.988
Well, Your Highness,

901
01:02:52.071 --> 01:02:55.199
I must say everything is going
just swimmingly.


902
01:02:55.450 --> 01:02:58.077
I knew you had it in you.

903
01:02:58.327 --> 01:03:00.413
-I let her go.

904
01:03:00.496 --> 01:03:01.581
Yes, yes.

905
01:03:01.914 --> 01:03:04.584
Splen...you what?

906
01:03:05.543 --> 01:03:08.463
-How could you do that?
-I had to.


907
01:03:08.921 --> 01:03:11.799
Yes, but-but-but... but why?

908
01:03:11.966 --> 01:03:15.011
Because I love her.

909
01:03:41.162 --> 01:03:44.874
<i>I was the one who had it all</i>

910
01:03:45.958 --> 01:03:49.670
<i>I was the master of my fate</i>

911
01:03:50.463 --> 01:03:55.259
<i>I never needed anybody in my life</i>

912
01:03:55.551 --> 01:03:59.305
<i>I learned the truth too late</i>

913
01:04:00.264 --> 01:04:03.559
<i>I'll never shake away the pain</i>

914
01:04:04.936 --> 01:04:08.397
<i>I close my eyes but she's still there</i>

915
01:04:09.816 --> 01:04:14.237
<i>I let her steal into my melancholy heart</i>

916
01:04:14.695 --> 01:04:19.700
<i>It's more than I can bear</i>

917
01:04:20.827 --> 01:04:25.373
<i>Now I know she'll never leave me</i>

918
01:04:25.832 --> 01:04:30.002
<i>Even as she runs away</i>

919
01:04:30.127 --> 01:04:32.672
<i>She will still torment me</i>

920
01:04:33.005 --> 01:04:39.595
<i>Calm me, hurt me</i>
<i>Move me, come what may</i>


921
01:04:39.929 --> 01:04:43.975
<i>Wasting in my lonely tower</i>

922
01:04:44.517 --> 01:04:48.855
<i>Waiting by an open door</i>

923
01:04:50.022 --> 01:04:52.608
<i>I'll fool myself, she'll walk right in</i>

924
01:04:54.819 --> 01:04:58.573
<i>And be with me for evermore</i>

925
01:05:31.814 --> 01:05:35.359
<i>I rage against the trials of love</i>

926
01:05:36.235 --> 01:05:40.156
<i>I curse the fading of the light</i>

927
01:05:40.698 --> 01:05:44.619
<i>Though she's already flown</i>
<i>So far beyond my reach</i>


928
01:05:45.077 --> 01:05:50.708
<i>She's never out of sight</i>

929
01:05:51.250 --> 01:05:55.796
<i>Now I know she'll never leave me</i>

930
01:05:56.005 --> 01:06:00.092
<i>Even as she fades from view</i>

931
01:06:00.593 --> 01:06:03.554
<i>She will still inspire me</i>

932
01:06:03.638 --> 01:06:09.769
<i>Be a part of everything I do</i>

933
01:06:10.144 --> 01:06:14.482
<i>Wasting in my lonely tower</i>

934
01:06:14.774 --> 01:06:19.195
<i>Waiting by an open door</i>

935
01:06:19.820 --> 01:06:22.782
<i>I'll fool myself, she'll walk right in</i>

936
01:06:24.200 --> 01:06:28.162
<i>And as the long, long nights begin</i>

937
01:06:28.537 --> 01:06:32.249
<i>I'll think of all that might have been</i>

938
01:06:32.375 --> 01:06:34.293
<i>Waiting here</i>

939
01:06:34.502 --> 01:06:41.425
<i>For evermore</i>

940
01:07:05.783 --> 01:07:08.119
What defines the legacy of a story?

941
01:07:08.661 --> 01:07:13.582
Its enduring impact both on
and off the screen for evermore.


942
01:07:14.583 --> 01:07:17.378
<i>Perhaps it's seeing</i>
<i>that story reinvented</i>


943
01:07:17.503 --> 01:07:21.090
<i>just as</i>Beauty and the Beast
<i>was in its ground-breaking,</i>


944
01:07:21.257 --> 01:07:23.926
<i>highly-acclaimed Broadway adaptation.</i>

945
01:07:25.011 --> 01:07:27.888
<i>Since then,</i>
<i>Disney Theatrical Productions</i>


946
01:07:27.972 --> 01:07:30.433
<i>under the direction</i>
<i>of its president and producer,</i>


947
01:07:30.516 --> 01:07:34.228
<i>Thomas Schumacher,</i>
<i>has forged a new chapter</i>


948
01:07:34.478 --> 01:07:37.898
<i>in the legacy</i>
<i>of this classic title,</i>


949
01:07:37.982 --> 01:07:41.068
<i>one that gave audiences</i>
<i>around the world</i>


950
01:07:41.193 --> 01:07:44.864
<i>a chance to fall in love</i>
<i>with these iconic characters</i>


951
01:07:44.947 --> 01:07:49.535
<i>all over again,</i>
<i>from India to Australia</i>


952
01:07:50.369 --> 01:07:52.455
<i>to the warm Footlights</i>
<i>in the West End</i>


953
01:07:52.788 --> 01:07:54.415
<i>and throughout the UK.</i>

954
01:07:56.792 --> 01:08:00.504
<i>Or perhaps the legacy</i>
<i>of this timeless classic</i>


955
01:08:00.588 --> 01:08:03.549
<i>is in witnessing the magical</i>
<i>spark of inspiration</i>


956
01:08:03.632 --> 01:08:06.802
<i>it ignites in artists,</i>
<i>in children</i>


957
01:08:06.969 --> 01:08:09.430
<i>who wish they could be</i>
<i>part of its world,</i>


958
01:08:09.638 --> 01:08:13.434
<i>and in grown-ups</i>
<i>who still dream of the same.</i>


959
01:08:15.311 --> 01:08:17.980
As for where
that legacy will go from here,


960
01:08:19.356 --> 01:08:20.775
only time will tell.

961
01:08:21.233 --> 01:08:24.445
But if you would care to make
a prediction,


962
01:08:24.987 --> 01:08:27.948
please, be our guest.

963
01:08:31.494 --> 01:08:32.411
Hi!

964
01:08:46.509 --> 01:08:48.552
It's all right, Papa.
I'm home.


965
01:08:50.137 --> 01:08:52.890
I thought I'd never see you again.

966
01:08:53.682 --> 01:08:55.184
I missed you so much.

967
01:08:55.434 --> 01:08:57.853
But the Beast... how did you escape?

968
01:08:57.978 --> 01:09:00.731
I didn't escape, Papa.
He...he let me go.


969
01:09:01.148 --> 01:09:04.318
-That horrible Beast?
-But he's different now, Papa.


970
01:09:04.735 --> 01:09:07.071
He's changed somehow.

971
01:09:12.326 --> 01:09:15.496
-Hi!
-Oh, a stowaway.


972
01:09:15.579 --> 01:09:18.624
Why, hello there, little fella.

973
01:09:18.958 --> 01:09:21.043
Didn't think I'd see you again.

974
01:09:21.293 --> 01:09:25.673
Belle, why'd you go away?
Don't you like us anymore?


975
01:09:26.173 --> 01:09:28.259
Oh, Chip, of course I do.

976
01:09:28.384 --> 01:09:29.593
-It's just that...

977
01:09:32.638 --> 01:09:36.142
-May I help you?
<i>-I've come to collect your father.</i>


978
01:09:36.225 --> 01:09:38.978
<i>-My father?</i>
<i>-Don't worry, mademoiselle.</i>


979
01:09:39.562 --> 01:09:42.481
-We'll take good care of him.

980
01:09:42.565 --> 01:09:46.193
-My father's not crazy.
-He was raving like a lunatic.


981
01:09:46.360 --> 01:09:49.738
-We all heard him, didn't we?

982
01:09:49.905 --> 01:09:51.365
-No!

983
01:09:51.448 --> 01:09:53.075
-I won't let you.
-Belle?


984
01:09:53.450 --> 01:09:56.120
Maurice.
Tell us again, old man.


985
01:09:56.412 --> 01:10:00.040
Just how big was the Beast?

986
01:10:00.124 --> 01:10:03.043
He was...I mean, he was...
he was enormous!


987
01:10:03.127 --> 01:10:07.131
I'd say at least 8...
no, more like 10 feet.


988
01:10:09.341 --> 01:10:11.802
Well, you don't get
much crazier than that.


989
01:10:13.137 --> 01:10:14.638
It's true, I tell you!

990
01:10:15.472 --> 01:10:17.057
-Get him out of here.

991
01:10:17.141 --> 01:10:18.350
Let go of me!

992
01:10:18.726 --> 01:10:20.769
No! You can't do this.

993
01:10:22.271 --> 01:10:25.399
Poor Belle.
It's a shame about your father.


994
01:10:25.482 --> 01:10:27.276
You know he's not crazy, Gaston.

995
01:10:27.443 --> 01:10:32.823
Mm, I might be able to clear up
this little misunderstanding, if...


996
01:10:33.073 --> 01:10:35.784
-If what?
-If you marry me.


997
01:10:36.160 --> 01:10:38.245
-What?
-One little word, Belle.


998
01:10:38.329 --> 01:10:39.788
That's all it takes.

999
01:10:39.872 --> 01:10:41.415
-Never.
-Have it your way.


1000
01:10:41.582 --> 01:10:43.667
Belle? Hey...

1001
01:10:44.001 --> 01:10:45.127
Let go of me.

1002
01:10:45.502 --> 01:10:48.005
My father's not crazy,
and I can prove it.


1003
01:10:48.297 --> 01:10:49.673
Show me the Beast!

1004
01:10:58.265 --> 01:11:00.100
The Beast will make off
with your children.


1005
01:11:00.768 --> 01:11:01.894
He'll come after them
in the night.


1006
01:11:01.977 --> 01:11:03.646
-No!
-Gaston is right!


1007
01:11:04.063 --> 01:11:07.942
Look at its sharp, cruel fangs.
It's threat to us all!


1008
01:11:08.317 --> 01:11:10.986
We're not safe until its head
is mounted on my wall.


1009
01:11:11.403 --> 01:11:14.448
-I say we kill the Beast!
-Yeah!


1010
01:11:14.531 --> 01:11:16.450
No! I won't let you do this.

1011
01:11:16.533 --> 01:11:18.369
The monster must have her
under his spell.


1012
01:11:18.535 --> 01:11:20.537
He'll curse us all
if we don't stop him.


1013
01:11:21.038 --> 01:11:23.082
-Yeah!
-If you're not with us...


1014
01:11:24.083 --> 01:11:25.834
-you're against us!

1015
01:11:25.918 --> 01:11:27.044
Bring the old man.

1016
01:11:27.253 --> 01:11:29.255
Get your hands off me!

1017
01:11:29.588 --> 01:11:32.466
We can't have them running off
to warn the creature.


1018
01:11:32.591 --> 01:11:33.884
-Let us out!

1019
01:11:35.344 --> 01:11:38.430
We'll rid the village of this Beast.
Who's with me?


1020
01:11:38.514 --> 01:11:40.516
Yeah!

1021
01:11:40.599 --> 01:11:42.142
<i>Through the mist</i>
<i>Through the woods</i>


1022
01:11:42.226 --> 01:11:43.769
<i>Through the darkness and the shadows</i>

1023
01:11:43.852 --> 01:11:46.814
<i>It's a nightmare</i>
<i>But it's one exciting ride</i>


1024
01:11:46.897 --> 01:11:50.150
<i>Say a prayer then we're there</i>
<i>At the drawbridge of a castle</i>


1025
01:11:50.234 --> 01:11:53.028
<i>And there's something</i>
<i>Truly terrible inside</i>


1026
01:11:53.404 --> 01:11:56.740
<i>It's a beast</i>
<i>He's got fangs, razor sharp ones</i>


1027
01:11:56.824 --> 01:11:59.660
<i>Massive paws</i>
<i>Killer claws for the feast</i>


1028
01:11:59.910 --> 01:12:03.038
<i>Hear him roar, see him foam</i>
<i>But we're not coming home</i>


1029
01:12:03.122 --> 01:12:04.832
<i>Till he's dead</i>

1030
01:12:05.082 --> 01:12:06.583
<i>-Good and dead</i>
-Yeah!


1031
01:12:06.750 --> 01:12:08.294
<i>-Kill the beast</i>
<i>-Mount your horse</i>


1032
01:12:08.377 --> 01:12:10.087
<i>Screw your courage</i>
<i>To the sticking place</i>


1033
01:12:10.170 --> 01:12:13.048
<i>We're counting on Gaston</i>
<i>To lead the way</i>


1034
01:12:13.215 --> 01:12:16.302
<i>Through the mist, through the wood</i>
<i>Where within a haunted castle</i>


1035
01:12:16.385 --> 01:12:19.430
<i>Something's lurking</i>
<i>That you don't see every day</i>


1036
01:12:19.722 --> 01:12:22.641
<i>It's a beast</i>
<i>One as tall as a mountain</i>


1037
01:12:22.975 --> 01:12:26.186
<i>We won't rest till he's good and deceased</i>

1038
01:12:26.270 --> 01:12:29.565
<i>Sally forth, tally ho</i>
<i>Grab your sword, grab your bow</i>


1039
01:12:29.648 --> 01:12:31.066
<i>Praise the Lord and here we go</i>

1040
01:12:31.150 --> 01:12:32.860
We'll lay siege to the castle.

1041
01:12:33.068 --> 01:12:35.154
<i>We don't like</i>
<i>What we don't understand</i>


1042
01:12:35.237 --> 01:12:36.447
<i>In fact it scares us</i>

1043
01:12:36.530 --> 01:12:39.283
<i>And this monster is mysterious at least</i>

1044
01:12:39.450 --> 01:12:42.786
<i>Bring your guns, bring your knives</i>
<i>Save your children and your wives</i>


1045
01:12:42.870 --> 01:12:45.664
<i>We'll save our village and our lives</i>

1046
01:12:45.873 --> 01:12:47.333
<i>We'll kill the beast</i>

1047
01:12:47.541 --> 01:12:49.710
Take whatever booty
you can find.


1048
01:12:49.793 --> 01:12:52.838
But remember,
the Beast is mine!


1049
01:12:52.921 --> 01:12:55.924
<i>Hearts ablaze, banners high</i>
<i>We go marching into battle</i>


1050
01:12:56.008 --> 01:12:59.011
<i>Unafraid although</i>
<i>The danger just increased</i>


1051
01:12:59.219 --> 01:13:02.181
<i>Raise your flag, sing the song</i>
<i>Here we come, we're 50 strong</i>


1052
01:13:02.264 --> 01:13:06.518
<i>And 50 Frenchmen can't be wrong</i>
<i>Let's kill the beast</i>


1053
01:13:26.830 --> 01:13:29.750
-Now!

1054
01:13:46.975 --> 01:13:49.103
Yes!

1055
01:13:53.732 --> 01:13:54.983
Here we go!

1056
01:13:58.695 --> 01:14:01.073
-What the devil?

1057
01:14:01.156 --> 01:14:02.408
Belle, look out!

1058
01:14:09.164 --> 01:14:11.458
You guys gotta try
this thing.


1059
01:14:13.669 --> 01:14:16.713
-Move, move, move, move.

1060
01:14:21.427 --> 01:14:23.137
And stay out.

1061
01:14:25.806 --> 01:14:27.349
Ugh.

1062
01:14:53.417 --> 01:14:54.626
Get up.

1063
01:14:56.879 --> 01:14:58.005
Get up!

1064
01:14:58.547 --> 01:15:01.842
What's the matter, Beast?

1065
01:15:01.925 --> 01:15:04.928
Too kind and gentle
to fight back?


1066
01:15:12.352 --> 01:15:13.770
BELLE:<i>No!</i>

1067
01:15:16.523 --> 01:15:19.735
-Belle...
-No, Gaston, don't!


1068
01:15:25.491 --> 01:15:26.658
Let's go, Philippe.

1069
01:15:41.924 --> 01:15:44.092
Come on out and fight.

1070
01:15:46.178 --> 01:15:49.014
Were you in love with her,
Beast?


1071
01:15:49.097 --> 01:15:51.475
Did you honestly think
she'd want you


1072
01:15:51.642 --> 01:15:53.727
when she had someone like me?

1073
01:16:05.906 --> 01:16:07.741
It's over, Beast.

1074
01:16:07.991 --> 01:16:09.868
Belle is mine!

1075
01:16:13.997 --> 01:16:16.959
Let me go. Let me go!

1076
01:16:17.042 --> 01:16:18.377
Please, don't hurt me.

1077
01:16:18.460 --> 01:16:20.254
I'll do anything. Anything!

1078
01:16:34.601 --> 01:16:37.104
-Get out.

1079
01:16:37.354 --> 01:16:38.397
Beast!

1080
01:16:39.314 --> 01:16:40.524
Belle?

1081
01:16:49.533 --> 01:16:50.701
Belle.

1082
01:16:56.748 --> 01:16:58.250
You came back.

1083
01:17:22.482 --> 01:17:23.567
Oh.

1084
01:17:37.372 --> 01:17:38.332
You...

1085
01:17:40.167 --> 01:17:43.462
-you came back.
-Of course I came back.


1086
01:17:43.962 --> 01:17:45.172
I couldn't let them...

1087
01:17:45.922 --> 01:17:47.716
Oh, this is all my fault.

1088
01:17:48.175 --> 01:17:50.802
-If only I'd gotten here sooner.
-Maybe...


1089
01:17:52.304 --> 01:17:54.556
it's better... it's better this way.

1090
01:17:54.640 --> 01:17:56.099
Don't talk like that.

1091
01:17:57.142 --> 01:17:59.519
-You'll be all right.

1092
01:17:59.603 --> 01:18:02.939
We're together now.
Everything's going to be fine. You'll see.


1093
01:18:03.815 --> 01:18:05.400
At...

1094
01:18:05.651 --> 01:18:06.777
at least...

1095
01:18:07.819 --> 01:18:09.279
I got to see you

1096
01:18:10.614 --> 01:18:12.074
one last time.

1097
01:18:23.043 --> 01:18:23.919
No.

1098
01:18:24.127 --> 01:18:25.212
No!

1099
01:18:26.129 --> 01:18:28.006
Please, please.

1100
01:18:28.590 --> 01:18:30.050
Please, don't leave me.

1101
01:18:33.929 --> 01:18:35.222
I love you.

1102
01:20:54.402 --> 01:20:56.947
Belle. It's me!

1103
01:21:12.838 --> 01:21:14.256
It is you!

1104
01:21:47.372 --> 01:21:50.584
Lumière. Cogsworth!

1105
01:21:51.209 --> 01:21:53.545
Oh! Mrs. Potts!

1106
01:21:53.879 --> 01:21:55.839
-Look at us!

1107
01:21:55.964 --> 01:21:57.549
Mama, mama!

1108
01:22:01.595 --> 01:22:03.763
-Oh, my goodness.

1109
01:22:04.014 --> 01:22:05.724
-It is a miracle!

1110
01:22:48.350 --> 01:22:52.687
<i>Tale as old as time</i>

1111
01:22:54.648 --> 01:22:59.235
<i>True as it can be</i>

1112
01:23:01.237 --> 01:23:03.823
<i>Barely even friends</i>

1113
01:23:04.157 --> 01:23:11.122
<i>Then somebody bends unexpectedly</i>

1114
01:23:13.249 --> 01:23:16.294
<i>Just a little change</i>

1115
01:23:16.503 --> 01:23:19.047
<i>Just a little change</i>

1116
01:23:19.255 --> 01:23:22.342
<i>Small to say the least</i>

1117
01:23:22.634 --> 01:23:25.512
<i>Both a little scared</i>

1118
01:23:25.595 --> 01:23:28.348
<i>Neither one prepared</i>

1119
01:23:28.598 --> 01:23:34.771
<i>Beauty and the Beast</i>

1120
01:23:35.021 --> 01:23:39.859
<i>Ever just the same</i>

1121
01:23:41.361 --> 01:23:46.866
<i>Ever a surprise</i>

1122
01:23:47.450 --> 01:23:50.578
<i>Ever as before</i>

1123
01:23:50.662 --> 01:23:53.498
<i>Ever just as sure</i>

1124
01:23:53.748 --> 01:23:59.004
<i>As the sun will rise</i>

1125
01:24:09.222 --> 01:24:12.392
<i>Oh!</i>

1126
01:24:37.250 --> 01:24:40.503
<i>Certain as the sun</i>

1127
01:24:40.587 --> 01:24:43.673
H.E.R.: <i>Certain as the sun</i>

1128
01:24:43.757 --> 01:24:46.968
<i>Rising in the east</i>

1129
01:24:47.052 --> 01:24:50.221
